data.description: This is a Wonderful 2/2 bungalow on a mature treed lot.  The home has been very well-maintained and has brand new carpet and paint. This is a split bedroom design with easy access to each bathroom from each bedroom. When standing in the kitchen, you overlook the living room and dining room area. Very open floor plan and laid out very well. There's a good flow in this home. Enjoy your morning coffee on the back patio that is covered and overlooks your fenced backyard plus a storage building.  Don’t let this one pass you by! New roof installed in Aug 2023.
